---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Ruta: Software Testing" description="Ruta profesional de software testing: del testing manual a la automatización con IA.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
    <nav class="text-sm text-content-muted mb-6">
      <a href="/rutas" class="hover:text-content">Rutas</a> / <span class="text-content">Software Testing</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">Ruta: Software Testing</h1>
      <p class="text-content-muted mb-6 md:mb-8 text-base md:text-lg">
        Convertite en un QA engineer completo. Desde las bases del testing manual hasta automatización avanzada e inteligencia artificial aplicada al aseguramiento de calidad.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Objetivo profesional</h2>
      <p class="text-content-muted mb-8">QA Engineer / Test Automation Engineer / QA Lead</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Nivel de entrada</h2>
      <p class="text-content-muted mb-8">Sin experiencia previa requerida.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Progresión</h2>
      <ol class="space-y-4 mb-8">
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-bg-elevated text-brand font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-sm">1</span>
          <div>
            <a href="/programas/testing-manual-software" class="font-semibold text-brand hover:underline">Testing Manual de Software</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-content-muted">Fundamentos, diseño de pruebas, gestión de defectos.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-bg-elevated text-brand font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-sm">2</span>
          <div>
            <a href="/programas/automatizacion-pruebas-software" class="font-semibold text-brand hover:underline">Automatización de Pruebas</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-content-muted">Selenium, Cypress, CI/CD, scripting.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-bg-elevated text-brand font-bold flex items-center justify-center text-sm">3</span>
          <div>
            <a href="/programas/testing-software-ia-sistemas-inteligentes" class="font-semibold text-brand hover:underline">Testing con IA y Sistemas Inteligentes</a>
            <p class="text-sm text-content-muted">IA aplicada al testing, análisis predictivo, generación automática de pruebas.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Tecnologías</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8">
        <span class="glass text-content-secondary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm">Selenium</span>
        <span class="glass text-content-secondary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm">Cypress</span>
        <span class="glass text-content-secondary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm">Playwright</span>
        <span class="glass text-content-secondary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm">Postman</span>
        <span class="glass text-content-secondary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm">Python</span>
        <span class="glass text-content-secondary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm">JavaScript</span>
        <span class="glass text-content-secondary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm">Jenkins</span>
        <span class="glass text-content-secondary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm">GitHub Actions</span>
      </div>

      <a href="/admision/solicitar-informacion" class="btn-primary inline-block rounded-full bg-brand text-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-brand-hover transition-all duration-300">
        Empezar esta ruta
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
